      "text": [
        " : «مَوْضِعُ قَبْرِ اَلْحُسَيْنِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ مُنْذُ يَوْمَ دُفِنَ فِيهِ رَوْضَةٌ مِنْ رِيَاضِ اَلْجَنَّةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3165 - Ishaq ibn Ammar has narrated from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) who said:\n\"The site of the grave of Husayn (as) has been, since the day he was buried there, a garden from the gardens of Paradise.\""
        ]
